songs.title: Right Now
songs.lyrics:
[Verse?]
...bought me a couple things I wanted
Like fuck it, I'ma ball, right?

[Bridge?}
You see you can't keep fighting me
Like a real [unknown]
[...]
...never lost what I felt when us first started

[Chorus?]
Right now, I gotta be selfish (gotta be)
Right now, babe, I can't help it
Right now...
